 der Boden der Inhumanität". In diesem Buch verbindet der Autor dieses Plädoyer mit biografischen Notizen und einer Schilderung seiner eigenen Tätigkeit in Forschung, Klinik und Lehre der Inneren Medizin. Im Vordergrund seiner 50-jährigen Berufstätigkeit stand dabei immer die Suche nach wissenschaftlichen Belegen für das ärztliche Handeln.  aMedicine’s commitment to science is a precondition for humane medicine, this book argues. The author links this conviction to biographical sketches and a description of his personal work in research, clinical care, and the teaching of internal medicine. The scientific grounding of medical practice has been a consistent focus of the author for over fifty years.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Mai 2021) 4aArzneimittelbewertung. 4aBiographie. 4aDGIM. 4aDiabetes mellitus. 4aDiagnoseevaluierung. 7aMEDICAL / Clinical Medicine.2bisacsh  aBiography.  aGerman Society for Internal Medicine.  adiabetes mellitus.  adiagnostic evaluation.  adrug assessment.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Ebook Package 2020z978311069627108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2020z9783110704518oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Medicine and Life Sciences 2020z9783110704600oZDB-23-DPM0 cEPUBz97831106766170 cprintz978311067655640uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311067659440uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110676594423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783110676594.jpg  a978-3-11-069627-1  DG Ebook Package 2020b2020  aEBA_CL_MDPM  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2020  aZDB-23-DPMb2020